message.entry: M must be a scalar positive integer.
M must be in the form of M = 2^K, where K is a positive integer.
INI_PHASE must be a real scalar.
Symbol order vector must have M elements.
Symbol order vector is only supported for Square QAM.
OutputType must be Bit for fixed-point input.
M must be an even power of two for fixed-point input.
Input must be a matrix or an array with 3 dimensions.
Fixed-point input must be a signed, fixed-point fi object.
M must be less than or equal to 1024 for fixed-point output.
INI_PHASE is not supported in this form.
The number of elements in noise variance vector must be equal to the size of the last dimension of input Y.
Input Y must be of datatype double or single when ''OutputType'' is ''{0}''.
